full_text: Screened by NARA, 8/17/2023 OMB APPROVAL NO. 1405-0015 EXPIRES: 8-31-92 ESTIMATED BURDEN: 1 HOUR APPLICATION FOR IMMIGRANT VISA ANL GISTRATION PART I - BIOGRAPHIC DATA INSTRUCTIONS: Complete one copy of this form for yourself and each member of your family, regardless of age, who will immigrate with you. Please print or type your answer to all questions. Questions that are Not Applicable should be so marked. If there is insufficient room on the form, answer on a separate sheet using the same numbers as appear on the form. Attach the sheet to this form. WARNING: Any false statement or concealment of a material fact may result in your permanent explusion from the United States.
